usdSonetAgent.name: usdSonetAgent

revisions.description: Separate out the SONET VT support.
The initial release of this management information module.

usdSonetAgent.contactinfo: Unisphere Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 E-mail: mib@UnisphereNetworks.com
usdSonetAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the SONET component of the SNMP agent in the Unisphere Routing Switch family of products.

usdSonetAgentV1.name: usdSonetAgentV1
usdSonetAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the SONET component of the Unisphere Routing Switch SNMP
        agent.  This version of the SONET component was supported in the
        Unisphere RX 1.x system releases.
usdSonetAgentV1.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the SONET application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when support for the standard VT group was added.

usdSonetAgentV2.name: usdSonetAgentV2
usdSonetAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the SONET component of the Unisphere Routing Switch SNMP
        agent.  This version of the SONET component was supported in the
        Unisphere RX 2.x system releases.
usdSonetAgentV2.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the SONET application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when support for the proprietary path and VT groups were added.

usdSonetAgentV3.name: usdSonetAgentV3
usdSonetAgentV3.productrelease:
Version 3 of the SONET component of the Unisphere Routing Switch SNMP
        agent.  This version of the SONET component was supported in the
        Unisphere RX 3.0 and 3.1 system releases.
usdSonetAgentV3.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the SONET application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when support for the RFC-2558 version of the SONET-MIB and far-end statistics were added.

usdSonetAgentV4.name: usdSonetAgentV4
usdSonetAgentV4.productrelease:
Version 4 of the SONET component of the Unisphere Routing Switch SNMP
        agent.  This version of the SONET component was supported in the
        Unisphere RX 3.2 system release.
usdSonetAgentV4.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the SONET application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when Virtual Tributary (VT) support was searated out into a separate capabilities statement.

usdSonetBasicAgentV1.name: usdSonetBasicAgentV1
usdSonetBasicAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the basic SONET component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  It does not include Virtual Tributary (VT) support.  This
        version of the basic SONET component is supported in the Unisphere RX
        3.3 and subsequent system releases.
usdSonetBasicAgentV1.description: The MIB conformance groups supported by the SNMP agent for the SONET application in the Unisphere Routing Switch.

usdSonetVTAgentV1.name: usdSonetVTAgentV1
usdSonetVTAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the SONET VT component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the SONET component is supported in the
        Unisphere RX 3.3 and subsequent system releases.
usdSonetVTAgentV1.description: The MIB conformance groups supported by the SNMP agent for the SONET application in the Unisphere Routing Switch.
